#: ../../getting_started/configure_kdenlive/configuration_colors+guides.rst:32
msgid "Colors and Guides"
msgstr "Colors i guies"

#: ../../getting_started/configure_kdenlive/configuration_colors+guides.rst:34
msgid ""
"This section is used to configure the colors used for audio thumbnails, the "
"monitor overlay and background color, and the grid for certain effects."
msgstr ""
"Aquesta secció s'utilitza per a configurar els colors utilitzats a les "
"miniatures d'àudio, la superposició del monitor i el color de fons, i la "
"quadrícula per a certs efectes."

#: ../../getting_started/configure_kdenlive/configuration_colors+guides.rst:36
msgid ""
"You can also add, edit, and delete the categories and colors used for Guides"
" and Markers."
msgstr ""
"També podeu afegir, editar i suprimir les categories i colors utilitzats per "
"a guies i marcadors."

#: ../../getting_started/configure_kdenlive/configuration_colors+guides.rst:43
msgid "The Colors and Guides section"
msgstr "La secció colors i guies"

# skip-rule: rst-menuselection
#: ../../getting_started/configure_kdenlive/configuration_colors+guides.rst:45
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Audio thumbnail colors` Click on the color bar to change the "
"color of the audio wave thumbnail. The color bar on the right controls the "
"color of the second channel (see the section "
":doc:`Timeline</getting_started/configure_kdenlive/configuration_timeline>` "
":menuselection:`--> Thumbnails -->` :guilabel:`Separate audio channels`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Colors de les miniatures d'àudio` Feu clic a la barra de color "
"per a canviar el color de la miniatura de l'ona d'àudio. La barra de color "
"de la dreta controla el color del segon canal (vegeu la secció :doc:`Línia de "
"temps </getting_started/configure_kdenlive/configuration_timeline>` "
":menuselection:`--> Miniatures -->` :guilabel:`Separa els canals d'àudio`)."

#: ../../getting_started/configure_kdenlive/configuration_colors+guides.rst:47
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Monitor overlay color` Click on the color bar to change the color"
" of the monitor overlay lines. See the chapter about the :ref:`ui-"
"monitors_display_toolbar`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Color de superposició del monitor` Feu clic a la barra de colors "
"per a canviar el color de les línies de superposició del monitor. See el "
"capítol sobre :ref:`ui-monitors_display_toolbar`."

#: ../../getting_started/configure_kdenlive/configuration_colors+guides.rst:49
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Monitor background color` Click on the color bar to change the "
"color of the monitor background."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Color de fons del monitor` Feu clic a la barra de colors per a "
"canviar el color de fons del monitor."

#: ../../getting_started/configure_kdenlive/configuration_colors+guides.rst:51
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Guides and Markers Categories` This lists all the defined "
"categories for Guides and Markers. From her you can add, edit, and delete "
"categories."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Categories de guies i marcadors` Llista totes les categories "
"definides de guies i marcadors. Des d'ella podeu afegir, editar i eliminar "
"categories."

#: ../../getting_started/configure_kdenlive/configuration_colors+guides.rst:53
msgid ""
"Click on :guilabel:`Add category` to add a new category. Select a color and "
"enter a name."
msgstr ""
"Feu clic a :guilabel:`Afegeix una categoria` per a afegir una categoria "
"nova. Seleccioneu un color i introduïu un nom."

#: ../../getting_started/configure_kdenlive/configuration_colors+guides.rst:55
msgid ""
"Select a category and click on :guilabel:`Edit category` or simply double-"
"click an existing one to change the color and/or the name."
msgstr ""
"Seleccioneu una categoria i feu clic a :guilabel:`Edita la categoria` o "
"simplement feu doble clic a una d'existent per a canviar el color i/o el nom."

#: ../../getting_started/configure_kdenlive/configuration_colors+guides.rst:57
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Delete category` to delete the selected category."
msgstr ""
"Feu clic a :guilabel:`Suprimeix la categoria` per a suprimir la categoria "
"seleccionada."

#: ../../getting_started/configure_kdenlive/configuration_colors+guides.rst:59
msgid ""
"The selected category will be deleted without any further confirmation and "
"will be effective immediately without the need to click on "
":guilabel:`Apply`. Even clicking :guilabel:`Cancel` or :guilabel:`Restore "
"Defaults` will not bring it back!"
msgstr ""
"La categoria seleccionada se suprimirà sense més confirmació i serà efectiva "
"immediatament sense necessitat de fer clic a :guilabel:`Aplica`. Fins i tot "
"en fer clic a :guilabel:`Cancel·la` o a :guilabel:`Restaura els valors "
"predeterminats` no la tornarà!"
